  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><i><b>Red Sands</b></i> is a text by Maester <a href=\"/index.php/Gareth_(maester)\" title=\"Gareth (maester)\">Gareth</a>, who chronicles several <a href=\"/index.php/Dorne\" title=\"Dorne\">Dornish</a> letters. Gareth suggests that Lord <a href=\"/index.php/House_Qorgyle\" title=\"House Qorgyle\">Qorgyle</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Sandstone\" title=\"Sandstone\">Sandstone</a> arranged the murder of Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Lyonel_Tyrell_(lord)\" title=\"Lyonel Tyrell (lord)\">Lyonel Tyrell</a> during King <a href=\"/index.php/Daeron_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Daeron I Targaryen\">Daeron I Targaryen</a>'s <a href=\"/index.php/Conquest_of_Dorne\" title=\"Conquest of Dorne\">conquest of Dorne</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_targaryen_kings:_daeron_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf_the_targaryen_kings:_daeron_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Red_Sands&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiaf_the_targaryen_kings:_daeron_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_targaryen_kings:_daeron_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, The Targaryen Kings: Daeron I.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached ti